<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Modern Blog Layout</title>

<style>

* {
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
    box-sizing: border-box;
}

body {
    font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
    background-color: #378a6b;
    line-height: 1.6;
}


header {
    background: #a2a74a;
    color: rgb(87, 16, 16);
    padding: 2rem 5%;
    text-align: center;
}

header h1 {
    font-size: 2rem;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
}


.main-container {
    padding: 3% 5%;
}


.blog-grid {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 2rem;
}


.blog-card {
    background: rgb(224, 230, 229);
    padding: 1.5rem;
    border: 1px solid #9d8585;
    border-radius: 8px;
    flex: 1 1 300px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: space-between;
    transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
}

.blog-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-5px);
    box-shadow: 0 8px 15px rgba(176, 156, 156, 0.1);
}

.blog-card h2 {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    color: #0a141e;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
}

.blog-card p {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: #3a3131;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
}


.read-btn {
    text-decoration: none;
    text-align: center;
    padding: 0.6rem;
    background: #185c88;
    color: white;
    border-radius: 5px;
    transition: background 0.3s ease;
}

.read-btn:hover {
    background: #2980b9;
}

</style>
</head>
<body>

<header>
    <h1>My Tech Blog</h1>
</header>

<div class="main-container">
    <div class="blog-grid">

        <div class="blog-card">
            <h2>Understanding Flexbox</h2>
            <p>Learn how Flexbox helps create modern responsive layouts easily and efficiently.</p>
            <a href="#" class="read-btn">Read More</a>
        </div>

        <div class="blog-card">
            <h2>CSS Grid Explained</h2>
            <p>A beginner-friendly guide to mastering CSS Grid for complex web layouts.</p>
            <a href="#" class="read-btn">Read More</a>
        </div>

        <div class="blog-card">
            <h2>Responsive Design Tips</h2>
            <p>Best practices to make your websites look perfect on all devices.</p>
            <a href="#" class="read-btn">Read More</a>
        </div>

        <div class="blog-card">
            <h2>Modern UI Trends</h2>
            <p>Explore the latest UI/UX design trends shaping the web industry.</p>
            <a href="#" class="read-btn">Read More</a>
        </div>

        <div class="blog-card">
            <h2>Web Performance Basics</h2>
            <p>Improve loading speed and optimize your website performance effectively.</p>
            <a href="#" class="read-btn">Read More</a>
        </div>

    </div>
</div>

</body>
</html>
